            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="rag-set" class="section">
      <h2>3. RAG Database Images — Fantasy Icon Set</h2>
      <h3>3.1 Image Overview</h3>
      <p>The Image Sets RAG library contains six square-format fantasy-themed icon graphics. These images appear to be screenshots of game assets, likely from avatar generators, RPG maker resource packs, or game UI overlays from around March 2023.</p>
      <p>All images share a common aesthetic: dark backgrounds, glowing auras, humanoid silhouettes, and fantasy or magical themes. None of the images contain text, numbers, charts, or data visualizations.</p>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Shared Characteristics</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Square icon format</li>
          <li>Fantasy or magical theme</li>
          <li>Human or humanoid silhouettes</li>
          <li>Glowing light effects</li>
          <li>Dark backgrounds</li>
