      <h3>3.3 Purpose and Use Cases</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Video game avatar or character icon</li>
        <li>Steam or gaming profile picture</li>
        <li>Twitch or streaming overlay asset</li>
        <li>RPG Maker or game asset pack</li>
        <li>Forum, Discord, or social media avatar</li>
        <li>Virtual tabletop (VTT) token</li>
        <li>Mobile game character select icon</li>
        <li>Fan art resource or asset pack</li>
      </ol>
      <p><strong>Most confident use case:</strong> Gaming profile avatar or in-game character icon.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="beach-photo" class="section">
      <h2>4. Beach Photograph — _IMG3766.JPG</h2>
      <h3>4.1 Image Overview</h3>
      <p><code>_IMG3766.JPG</code> is a natural outdoor photograph of a beach or coastal scene. It was uploaded by the user and processed through the system vision pipeline using the <code>thatdamai/moondream-1.8b:latest</code> model.</p>
      <p>The image was located in the project folder with a corresponding <code>.agent</code> markdown file, following the system naming convention in which ingested images generate a paired markdown file in the <code>.agent</code> folder.</p>

      <h3>4.2 Vision Model Description</h3>
      <blockquote class="card">
        The image shows a woman running on a beach, wearing a blue shirt and white shorts. She is carrying a backpack and appears to be in motion towards the right side of the frame. In the background, there are other people walking along the shoreline, some closer to the water's edge while others are further back. The sky above them is filled with clouds, suggesting an overcast day.
